		<hr size="1">There are many range items, and unless a bow has awesome stats, it's useless on a paladin.  I gave up using a bow in my 30's, if not late 20's.</P><P>Go to <A HREF="http://everquest.allakhazam.com" TARGET="_BLANK">http://everquest.allakhazam.com</A> and click BY SLOT under EQUIPMENT.  Then click RANGE (or RANGED).  Once this screen opens, change the drop box to PALADIN usuable only.  If you wish, you can even order the list by the stat you want to aim for more.<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
